[1] Spain: Spanish priest still suspect along with 5 others in Madrid
Date: Thu 16 Oct 2014
Source: Yahoo News [edited]
http://news.yahoo.com/madrid-airport-activates-protocol-over-suspected-ebola-case-120703763--finance.html

Priest, air passenger among 6 hospitalized in Spain for Ebola tests
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spanish authorities reported 4 new patients with suspected Ebola symptoms on Thu 16 Oct 2014], including a feverish passenger who started shaking on an Air France flight to Madrid and a Spanish priest who had recently been in Liberia; 3 of the cases were in the capital and the 4th in the Canary Islands, where a health source said 2 other people were admitted to hospital for precautionary monitoring.
[By Sarah White & Rodrigo De Miguel]
